  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the next step in the thing-- in which the thing become even harder, grimmer, and darker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lefted the city in train during the night, travel quite a long time in this very primitive trains, moving extremely slow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the horse or for animals transportation, wagons that were for transportation through of animals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was starting in Sofia, going north in a different direction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- during the night-- they used to, at certain location, to take also different directions the wagons, reconnected to a different trains going in different direction, always in north of Sofia, and most of them aimed to toward the cities or villages that were on the river Danube, obviously for easier transportation there.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the year early 1941, '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After, I understood that some of my cousins were also sended with the same three.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, took a long time before that I saw them already when we arrive on this village, Vidin, that this--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were perhaps three or four days there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A long time took this waiting for relocation of the trains and somewhere in the middle of the route.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So because the distance-- actually, there were not so great distances.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are pretty short distances.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, while possible to see if you are close to the door and the door is open, which was not very often.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But there was not so much what to see in the time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because basically, was winter season, cold, snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one person, what my mother always was trying that I and many mothers other, to preserve that the children don't become so sick that they die.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some, some of the children got sick there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
